WEBVTT

00:06.520 --> 00:07.986
(OUTRUN BROTHERS PICTURES)

00:14.077 --> 00:16.746
(Seo Ji Hye)

00:22.085 --> 00:24.220
(Go Soo)

00:30.994 --> 00:33.329
(Kim Jae Kyung)

00:38.434 --> 00:40.737
(Yoon Je Moon)

00:43.187 --> 00:45.788
(Written and Directed by Im Geon Jung)

00:47.384 --> 00:50.973
(REVERSE)

00:55.051 --> 00:55.885
(This drama is a work of fiction.)

00:55.885 --> 00:56.920
(All characters, organizations,
and events in this drama are fictitious.)

00:56.920 --> 00:57.754
(This drama complied
with production guidelines...)

00:57.754 --> 00:58.588
(for filming child actors and animals.)

01:39.562 --> 01:40.396
This is insane.

01:41.698 --> 01:42.632
Everyone's insane.

02:04.687 --> 02:06.656
Why is it so loud?

02:28.545 --> 02:29.379
Hee Su.

02:29.746 --> 02:30.580
Hee Su.

03:32.742 --> 03:35.645
(Accident)

03:44.487 --> 03:45.321
We have an emergency patient.

03:45.321 --> 03:47.023
She was conscious when she was rescued,

03:47.023 --> 03:48.758
but lost consciousness again
on the way here.

03:48.758 --> 03:50.026
Let's get her to the operating room now.

03:50.293 --> 03:51.861
- Call the surgeon on duty.
- Yes, Doctor.

03:51.861 --> 03:52.962
(Operating Center)

04:00.904 --> 04:03.072
Ma'am, can you hear me?

04:03.439 --> 04:04.374
Can you hear me?

04:12.482 --> 04:13.216
Sorry?

04:29.332 --> 04:32.302
(3 days after the accident)

04:44.747 --> 04:47.050
Myo Jin, wake up.

04:50.854 --> 04:51.921
Can you hear me?

04:54.524 --> 04:56.259
Jun Ho.

04:57.827 --> 04:58.561
Yes?

04:59.696 --> 05:00.730
Ryu...

05:03.066 --> 05:04.400
Jun Ho.

05:05.168 --> 05:06.002
Yeah.

05:07.871 --> 05:08.705
It's me.

05:09.572 --> 05:10.840
Ryu Jun Ho.

05:19.215 --> 05:20.149
Myo Jin.

05:51.514 --> 05:52.582
You bastard.

06:17.273 --> 06:20.210
(5 days after the accident)

06:27.116 --> 06:28.017
You're awake.

06:31.387 --> 06:33.256
How do you feel? Are you okay?

06:34.724 --> 06:36.159
Where...

06:37.827 --> 06:38.862
am I?

06:43.867 --> 06:45.201
You're in the hospital.

06:46.703 --> 06:48.838
You got hurt in an accident,
so you were admitted.

06:50.440 --> 06:53.877
You're probably
having trouble moving right now.

06:54.911 --> 06:56.079
An accident?

06:57.180 --> 06:58.014
Luckily,

06:59.816 --> 07:01.618
you're past the worst of it.

07:01.618 --> 07:02.619
They said...

07:02.919 --> 07:05.421
you pulled through
because you're strong and healthy.

07:07.290 --> 07:08.358
Myo Jin.

07:11.027 --> 07:11.861
Is that...

07:13.196 --> 07:14.631
my name?

07:15.832 --> 07:16.666
Yeah.

07:17.300 --> 07:18.168
Myo Jin.

07:19.102 --> 07:20.303
Ham Myo Jin.

07:21.604 --> 07:22.539
My fiancée.

07:27.010 --> 07:28.278
We're engaged.

07:30.947 --> 07:31.814
Do you remember?

07:33.483 --> 07:34.817
I don't remember...

07:36.586 --> 07:37.754
anything.

07:39.889 --> 07:40.723
It's okay.

07:41.424 --> 07:43.860
Yeah, that's perfectly normal right now.

07:44.694 --> 07:46.329
But it'll all slowly come back.

08:09.619 --> 08:11.321
Are you going...

08:11.321 --> 08:13.857
to keep standing there
like you're being punished?

08:16.426 --> 08:17.694
I like the view.

08:19.562 --> 08:20.697
For a Hwangryong orchid,

08:21.564 --> 08:23.399
you only water it once a week.

08:32.442 --> 08:33.276
Have a seat.

08:40.950 --> 08:41.751
Did you know?

08:42.852 --> 08:44.320
You've got this strange way...

08:45.355 --> 08:47.524
of drawing people's attention.

08:48.758 --> 08:50.627
With social media and all,

08:50.627 --> 08:53.329
isn't everyone desperate
for attention these days?

08:54.230 --> 08:55.064
But...

08:56.199 --> 08:58.034
you don't seem to need that.

09:00.303 --> 09:01.404
You're too kind.

09:02.172 --> 09:02.972
But...

09:03.806 --> 09:06.075
I like you for another reason.

09:06.776 --> 09:07.977
Do you know what it is?

09:08.378 --> 09:10.013
No, but I'd like to.

09:10.013 --> 09:11.080
Please tell me.

09:12.048 --> 09:13.616
Because I can feel your ambition.

09:16.152 --> 09:17.687
Any real man...

09:19.355 --> 09:22.158
ought to carry a sharp blade in here...

09:22.158 --> 09:23.126
like you.

09:25.228 --> 09:26.529
Pride and dignity,

09:26.930 --> 09:28.298
who gives a damn about that?

09:29.465 --> 09:30.366
Right?

09:34.971 --> 09:36.539
It's a real shame...

09:37.440 --> 09:38.575
Chairman Choi died like that.

09:39.843 --> 09:41.444
He was still in his prime.

09:44.547 --> 09:46.783
It must be hard on you too.

09:58.361 --> 10:01.631
This is the list of judges
finalized yesterday.

10:02.165 --> 10:02.999
Thank you.

10:03.800 --> 10:05.768
Now that it's in my hands,

10:05.768 --> 10:08.004
it reaching someone else's hands...

10:08.004 --> 10:10.039
is only a matter of time.

10:10.473 --> 10:13.543
How you clear a path is up to you.

10:15.178 --> 10:16.212
I'll remember that.

10:17.580 --> 10:21.518
I wondered how to repay
what I owed Chairman Choi,

10:23.820 --> 10:24.921
so make it count.

10:33.129 --> 10:35.798
(List of Judges
for the Museum Competition Released)

10:45.575 --> 10:47.610
I knew the lineup would be strong,

10:48.545 --> 10:49.846
but this is completely unexpected.

10:51.848 --> 10:54.851
Once people hear
CEO Oh Sang Il is judging,

10:54.851 --> 10:56.753
nobody's going to sleep easily.

10:57.554 --> 10:59.255
Me included, of course.

11:00.056 --> 11:01.457
CEO Oh Sang Il?

11:02.659 --> 11:03.526
Yes.

11:03.993 --> 11:06.162
He's known for being incredibly rigid,

11:07.997 --> 11:10.300
so he doesn't usually do things like this.

11:11.100 --> 11:12.769
The International Federation
of Architects...

11:13.336 --> 11:15.405
hails him as the only person in Asia...

11:15.405 --> 11:16.673
who inspires them.

11:20.677 --> 11:21.978
I'll take you to the hospital.

11:22.712 --> 11:25.181
How is she feeling?

11:27.183 --> 11:28.551
The other injuries...

11:29.552 --> 11:31.421
seem to be healing well, but...

11:34.290 --> 11:38.127
I'd like to ask about my guardian,

11:38.127 --> 11:39.062
Ryu Jun Ho.

11:39.863 --> 11:41.764
They say he's the man I love.

11:41.764 --> 11:42.465
(30 days after the accident)

11:42.465 --> 11:44.100
But I can't remember him at all.

11:45.201 --> 11:46.836
Even after such a terrible accident,

11:46.836 --> 11:49.639
how can I not remember
the man I was engaged to?

11:50.139 --> 11:52.642
Is it frustrating
because your memories with Ryu Jun Ho...

11:52.642 --> 11:53.676
won't come back?

11:54.811 --> 11:57.947
It feels more like emotion.

11:59.249 --> 12:02.318
I know how much he worries about me
and how good he is to me,

12:02.919 --> 12:04.654
but I don't feel anything.

12:05.421 --> 12:07.156
My emotions feel distant.

12:08.024 --> 12:09.592
Since when have you felt that way?

12:11.127 --> 12:13.329
Ever since I woke up,

12:13.897 --> 12:15.632
it's felt the same.

12:17.233 --> 12:19.936
I tried to think
about what it was like before,

12:21.571 --> 12:23.239
but nothing comes to mind.

12:24.707 --> 12:26.643
Why am I like this?

12:28.912 --> 12:31.514
(Hanguk Somang Hospital)

12:45.261 --> 12:46.329
I have good news.

12:47.463 --> 12:48.331
What is it?

12:49.699 --> 12:50.533
This.

12:52.635 --> 12:54.537
They said you won't need it next week.

12:57.307 --> 12:59.275
I heard I'd need it longer.

13:01.377 --> 13:02.478
They said...

13:03.146 --> 13:06.015
your recovery is twice as fast
as everyone else's.

13:06.916 --> 13:07.817
I see.

13:11.821 --> 13:12.689
Thank you.

13:14.891 --> 13:15.725
For what?

13:16.159 --> 13:18.328
If anything had happened to you,

13:18.328 --> 13:19.195
I really would've...

13:21.331 --> 13:22.732
It's thanks to you, Jun Ho.

13:23.266 --> 13:24.133
Thank you.

13:28.238 --> 13:31.007
Episodic memory loss?

13:31.474 --> 13:34.611
It's when the brain
creates a defense mechanism...

13:34.611 --> 13:36.613
against anxiety.

13:37.213 --> 13:39.048
It happens unconsciously...

13:39.048 --> 13:41.251
regardless of the person's will,

13:41.751 --> 13:44.387
and it's often seen
in people who've suffered...

13:44.387 --> 13:45.688
severe trauma.

13:46.556 --> 13:48.725
It seems...

13:49.893 --> 13:52.462
she still can't remember me clearly.

13:52.929 --> 13:53.696
Yes.

13:54.497 --> 13:55.665
Ms. Ham still feels...

13:56.499 --> 13:59.636
even you are a stranger.

14:00.436 --> 14:04.774
But it's already been a month
since treatment began.

14:05.608 --> 14:07.210
The fact...

14:07.210 --> 14:09.712
that she still can't clearly remember
even the man she's engaged to,

14:10.580 --> 14:14.317
isn't that very serious?

14:14.317 --> 14:15.084
No.

14:15.084 --> 14:16.619
Right now, to Ms. Ham,

14:16.619 --> 14:18.988
everyone around her
feels exactly the same.

14:19.255 --> 14:21.758
That's how severe the shock was.

14:21.758 --> 14:23.526
She sees me every day...

14:23.893 --> 14:25.695
and talks to me every day.

14:26.496 --> 14:27.397
How could she...

14:28.031 --> 14:30.333
feel the same about me
as she does about everyone else?

14:32.602 --> 14:35.538
Is that even possible?

14:48.384 --> 14:49.552
(Complete bed rest)

14:56.826 --> 14:57.994
According to the accident report,

14:58.461 --> 15:01.097
Ms. Ham was driving alone before dawn...

15:01.097 --> 15:03.066
when the car rolled over.

15:04.701 --> 15:06.603
No matter how strong someone is,

15:06.603 --> 15:10.473
the fear of death in that situation
must have been overwhelming.

15:11.875 --> 15:13.009
Just hang in there.

15:14.711 --> 15:15.912
Everything will be okay.

16:11.301 --> 16:13.203
Is this really all you've got?

16:13.203 --> 16:15.038
Shut up, you murdering bastard.

16:24.647 --> 16:26.282
Come on, give me more.

16:38.661 --> 16:39.495
Kill me.

16:42.532 --> 16:43.867
If you don't kill me today,

16:44.467 --> 16:45.535
then you're the one who dies...

16:46.369 --> 16:47.570
by my hand.

16:49.672 --> 16:52.642
How did you end up like this?

16:53.910 --> 16:54.878
Give up.

16:55.178 --> 16:56.746
You're beyond saving.

16:57.080 --> 16:58.948
Stop wasting your time.

16:58.948 --> 17:00.083
Are you done barking?

17:18.234 --> 17:19.135
Are you okay?

17:21.271 --> 17:22.105
Yes.

17:22.939 --> 17:23.873
Do you want some water?

17:25.608 --> 17:26.543
No.

17:35.318 --> 17:36.252
How does it feel?

17:37.086 --> 17:38.021
How does what feel?

17:38.388 --> 17:39.255
Finally,

17:40.323 --> 17:42.692
you're getting out
of this miserable hospital.

17:45.495 --> 17:46.930
No more patient gowns.

17:47.897 --> 17:50.133
You can wear clothes
that actually suit you.

18:13.857 --> 18:15.291
This must be a tricky one for you.

18:23.299 --> 18:24.701
This won't do.

18:25.368 --> 18:27.170
I need to rebuild the gallery.

18:28.505 --> 18:29.372
All of a sudden?

18:29.606 --> 18:31.341
I gave the exterior a vintage look,

18:31.341 --> 18:32.976
and trendy work won't come in now.

18:33.643 --> 18:35.011
People are judging it in advance.

18:36.012 --> 18:37.046
It has to change...

18:37.914 --> 18:39.048
starting with my own ideas.

18:39.983 --> 18:41.184
Do you have something in mind?

18:41.885 --> 18:44.954
Installation art and pop art are hot
in Korea right now.

18:45.555 --> 18:47.123
More people are majoring in them too.

18:48.424 --> 18:49.893
The gallery should change with that.

18:54.230 --> 18:55.265
But what brings you here?

18:55.532 --> 18:57.033
CEO Ryu is always busy.

18:59.536 --> 19:00.703
The museum competition.

19:01.437 --> 19:02.372
You've heard about it, right?

19:02.572 --> 19:03.406
Yeah.

19:04.207 --> 19:05.608
It looked pretty big.

19:06.042 --> 19:07.977
People are going to pull strings
with the assemblyman.

19:07.977 --> 19:10.713
Anyone who knows
he has clout at the ministry.

19:10.914 --> 19:13.149
Dad hasn't said anything yet.

19:13.816 --> 19:16.186
Why? Are you entering too?

19:16.753 --> 19:19.422
For an architect like me,
it's a dream stage...

19:20.190 --> 19:21.357
I cannot give up on.

19:23.193 --> 19:25.528
It's not about credentials or background,

19:26.596 --> 19:27.730
and definitely not money.

19:28.898 --> 19:30.400
So what's the real reason?

19:32.836 --> 19:35.672
It's like you turning down countless
offers from major corporations...

19:35.672 --> 19:38.541
and sitting here questioning who you are.

19:38.541 --> 19:39.409
Of course,

19:39.409 --> 19:42.412
it doesn't compare to the depth of insight
of a four-term assemblyman's daughter.

19:43.146 --> 19:44.347
Cut the jokes.

19:45.315 --> 19:46.449
What is it, then?

19:47.183 --> 19:48.218
A declaration.

19:50.720 --> 19:53.890
A declaration to step out
from Mono Group's shadow?

19:55.258 --> 19:56.359
Is that too grand?

19:57.560 --> 19:59.529
Then I just need to swat away the flies.

20:02.498 --> 20:05.001
(Hanguk Somang Hospital)

20:07.670 --> 20:10.540
(60 days after the accident)

20:13.543 --> 20:14.777
Nice weather, isn't it?

20:14.777 --> 20:16.079
You're finally being discharged.

20:16.412 --> 20:17.413
How do you feel?

20:18.281 --> 20:19.315
I'm fine.

20:19.516 --> 20:21.818
Is there anything
that's still especially uncomfortable?

20:22.452 --> 20:23.553
No.

20:23.553 --> 20:24.654
Everything's fine.

20:25.955 --> 20:26.823
Myo Jin.

20:28.057 --> 20:29.425
You're here.

20:29.425 --> 20:31.194
You've worked hard.

20:31.728 --> 20:34.931
Not me.
Myo Jin's the one who really suffered.

20:35.732 --> 20:37.600
Myo Jin, you've been through a lot.

20:42.739 --> 20:44.407
(Cognitive Function Test Record,
Ham Myo Jin)

20:44.407 --> 20:47.477
We've run cognitive tests over time,

20:48.144 --> 20:51.915
and you have severe impairment
in your pre-accident memories, Ms. Ham.

20:52.482 --> 20:54.984
Even after discharge,
you need to focus on treatment.

20:55.618 --> 20:56.653
Understood.

20:58.221 --> 21:01.658
Then what kind of effort
should she make day to day...

21:01.658 --> 21:03.326
to help her recovery?

21:03.626 --> 21:06.663
Get in the habit
of taking notes or making recordings.

21:06.663 --> 21:09.465
Sometimes, memories
can surface unexpectedly.

21:09.866 --> 21:10.967
When that happens,

21:10.967 --> 21:13.236
just accept them as they are.

21:13.870 --> 21:15.939
Even if they seem irrelevant now,

21:16.472 --> 21:18.875
they may be part of an important memory.

21:19.409 --> 21:22.512
Should I record them
every day, like a diary?

21:23.046 --> 21:25.548
Any method is fine,

21:25.548 --> 21:28.251
but it's best to act on it
as soon as possible.

21:41.564 --> 21:42.398
Myo Jin.

21:43.666 --> 21:44.767
Look behind you.

21:57.013 --> 21:58.014
Congratulations on your discharge.

21:59.582 --> 22:02.418
You have no idea how long I've waited...

22:02.418 --> 22:03.786
for this moment.

22:08.825 --> 22:09.893
Freesia.

22:10.393 --> 22:11.995
Right, freesia.

22:14.831 --> 22:16.232
Do you know what freesias mean?

22:19.569 --> 22:20.670
A new beginning.

22:21.871 --> 22:24.407
Here's to your new beginning.

22:25.608 --> 22:26.676
Thank you.

22:32.615 --> 22:34.984
I can remember flower names like this,

22:36.386 --> 22:38.555
so why can't I remember you, Jun Ho?

22:40.623 --> 22:41.624
Hello.

22:42.091 --> 22:44.994
I'm Ryu Jun Ho, Ham Myo Jin's fiancé.

22:45.428 --> 22:46.429
Nice to meet you.

22:51.301 --> 22:52.602
You can forget everything.

22:53.269 --> 22:55.138
I'm remembering it all for you.

22:56.372 --> 22:59.642
I'll keep filling it in
as much as you need.

23:00.243 --> 23:01.077
But...

23:02.145 --> 23:03.980
I'll fill you only with memories of me,

23:03.980 --> 23:05.315
and just ignore everything else.

23:48.958 --> 23:50.460
My room is across the hall.

23:50.994 --> 23:52.629
That'll be more comfortable
for a while, right?

23:54.264 --> 23:55.031
What?

23:56.966 --> 23:59.035
At the hospital,
I fell asleep beside you...

23:59.836 --> 24:01.571
and ended up with bruises
around my eyes a few times.

24:20.990 --> 24:21.991
Even now,

24:22.992 --> 24:25.962
minimalist designs are still in style.

24:26.629 --> 24:29.098
At a glance, they all look alike
because of the size,

24:29.098 --> 24:30.500
but if you look closely,
they're all different.

24:31.501 --> 24:34.704
They use wood or metal as materials...

24:35.338 --> 24:37.407
to show each one's character.

24:39.976 --> 24:41.945
They're very clean on their own,

24:41.945 --> 24:42.779
but...

24:43.913 --> 24:45.215
whether they really suit this place...

24:49.786 --> 24:50.587
Why?

24:53.423 --> 24:56.292
It just feels real now
that you're an architect, Jun Ho.

24:57.994 --> 25:00.530
Was I talking about something too boring?

25:00.530 --> 25:01.698
No.

25:02.632 --> 25:05.768
Then did you design
your house too, Jun Ho?

25:08.571 --> 25:09.472
Ours.

25:11.074 --> 25:11.908
Our house.

25:16.613 --> 25:18.047
Our house.

25:44.440 --> 25:47.110
Let's get you better soon
and go abroad too.

25:48.044 --> 25:49.479
I think that'd lift your spirits.

25:50.446 --> 25:51.247
Okay.

25:51.848 --> 25:53.816
Start thinking about
where you want to go...

25:53.816 --> 25:55.084
so I can prepare in advance.

25:56.553 --> 25:57.587
Prepare what?

25:57.921 --> 25:59.656
You've never been abroad...

26:00.089 --> 26:01.324
so you don't have a passport.

26:03.526 --> 26:04.527
I see.

26:08.898 --> 26:10.700
Myo Jin, can you pass me that bottle?

26:11.968 --> 26:13.336
I want to get rid of the meat smell.

26:14.671 --> 26:15.572
Here.

26:24.948 --> 26:25.682
Myo Jin.

26:26.549 --> 26:28.151
Myo Jin, are you okay?

26:30.220 --> 26:32.422
There was someone in the fire.

26:35.058 --> 26:36.059
Jun Ho.

26:37.260 --> 26:38.962
What happened to me?

26:42.799 --> 26:44.834
Any memory is fine.

26:44.834 --> 26:46.469
Just say whatever comes to you.

26:47.036 --> 26:49.205
A special anniversary or memory.

26:50.206 --> 26:52.408
Something you cherished.

26:53.376 --> 26:55.245
Someone you miss terribly,

26:55.245 --> 26:56.346
or...

26:56.346 --> 26:58.281
someone you never want to see again.

27:00.583 --> 27:01.518
A man.

27:03.887 --> 27:06.723
He's saying something loudly.

27:07.257 --> 27:09.492
Can you tell me...

27:09.492 --> 27:10.760
where you are?

27:13.196 --> 27:16.099
I don't know where it is.

27:17.133 --> 27:19.569
How do you feel there right now?

27:20.236 --> 27:22.005
I'm trapped.

27:23.540 --> 27:25.942
I want to get out, but I can't.

27:28.711 --> 27:31.514
It feels like I'm being dragged somewhere.

27:31.948 --> 27:33.283
Why does it feel that way?

27:33.850 --> 27:36.419
I feel like I did something wrong.

27:46.196 --> 27:47.030
Here.

27:58.908 --> 28:00.176
Would you take a look at this?

28:04.814 --> 28:06.349
The accident you experienced...

28:06.349 --> 28:08.251
is classified as an episodic memory.

28:08.885 --> 28:11.988
Anyone can lose memories after a shock.

28:12.622 --> 28:15.558
What you lost isn't the memory itself.

28:15.558 --> 28:18.528
The part that lets you retrieve it
was injured.

29:27.463 --> 29:28.631
Someone collapsed!

29:30.300 --> 29:31.334
Hey.

29:31.334 --> 29:32.402
- Hey, are you okay?
- Are you okay?

29:32.836 --> 29:34.337
Stay with us.

29:34.337 --> 29:35.171
Hey!

29:35.672 --> 29:37.240
This young guy...

29:41.311 --> 29:43.246
Boss, what did I tell you?

29:44.013 --> 29:45.682
I said she wouldn't die that easily.

29:46.716 --> 29:47.917
Now that she's out of the hospital,

29:47.917 --> 29:49.919
it's only a matter of time
before she comes looking for you.

29:51.321 --> 29:52.422
What are you going to do?

29:55.058 --> 29:58.661
Please stop being so stubborn
and listen to me.

30:09.372 --> 30:11.975
(Medicine)

30:41.204 --> 30:43.139
What are you so calm about?

30:44.174 --> 30:45.341
Boss,

30:45.808 --> 30:48.111
you don't think this is over, do you?

30:48.878 --> 30:50.480
"They've done all they can."

30:50.480 --> 30:52.348
"So maybe they won't do
anything else now."

30:53.049 --> 30:55.618
The moment you think that,
you'll get hit the same way again.

31:16.506 --> 31:17.807
Do you remember that flower's name too?

31:18.575 --> 31:20.276
You made that yourself, Myo Jin.

31:22.378 --> 31:23.213
I did?

31:24.180 --> 31:25.114
When?

31:26.749 --> 31:28.084
I'm not sure.

31:29.252 --> 31:30.954
Judging by how faded the color is,

31:31.521 --> 31:32.889
it must be old.

31:40.196 --> 31:42.098
Here, it's a new phone.

31:44.434 --> 31:45.702
I'm number one in it,

31:46.035 --> 31:47.203
so call me anytime.

31:49.005 --> 31:49.839
Okay.

31:55.778 --> 31:57.180
I know this is frustrating.

31:58.181 --> 32:00.583
It feels like
things will never get better, right?

32:01.684 --> 32:02.652
But they will.

32:03.219 --> 32:04.454
You'll get better soon.

32:05.622 --> 32:07.790
It won't be as hard
as it was in the hospital.

32:08.791 --> 32:10.159
I'll make sure of that.

32:23.640 --> 32:24.541
I'm sorry.

32:25.975 --> 32:27.143
It's okay.

32:27.143 --> 32:28.578
You're busy. Don't push yourself.

32:30.180 --> 32:32.549
I got everything ready
so we could go biking together.

32:34.083 --> 32:35.051
How about this weekend?

32:36.219 --> 32:37.287
Since it's been a while,

32:37.287 --> 32:39.422
I think I'd rather go out by myself.

32:41.824 --> 32:42.792
Are you sure about that?

32:43.226 --> 32:44.160
Why?

32:44.727 --> 32:46.563
You think I won't be able
to find my way home?

33:17.060 --> 33:19.128
What? She looks perfectly fine.

33:36.613 --> 33:38.715
I'm always by your side, Myo Jin.

33:39.649 --> 33:41.217
Whenever you look at this ring,

33:43.353 --> 33:45.021
I want you to think of me.

33:52.629 --> 33:53.396
Hey.

33:54.797 --> 33:55.598
Let go!

33:55.999 --> 33:58.067
Let go! Let go of my bag!

34:12.382 --> 34:13.316
Are you crazy?

34:13.983 --> 34:15.084
You little...

34:26.262 --> 34:27.197
Dang.

34:27.864 --> 34:28.731
Hey.

34:29.666 --> 34:31.134
- Unbelievable.
- Hey.

34:31.134 --> 34:33.136
You hit the jackpot.

34:33.136 --> 34:34.304
Don't touch it.

34:34.704 --> 34:35.805
Drinks are on me today.

34:42.712 --> 34:43.479
Hey.

34:43.813 --> 34:44.614
Hey.

34:44.614 --> 34:46.115
Just play your game, you punk.

34:46.115 --> 34:47.550
Look over there, idiot.

34:47.917 --> 34:48.785
Hey, over there.

34:49.919 --> 34:50.753
Hey.

35:16.513 --> 35:17.413
Architecture...

35:18.214 --> 35:21.751
begins when two bricks
are carefully put together.

35:22.852 --> 35:24.821
That's how it begins.

35:26.689 --> 35:28.358
At last year's Copenhagen conference,

35:28.358 --> 35:30.226
that's the line Mr. Oh quoted.

35:30.760 --> 35:32.428
That's exactly how I feel right now.

35:33.229 --> 35:35.965
Don't tell me you've memorized
Mr. Oh's whole speech from that day.

35:37.133 --> 35:38.401
How much time do we have?

35:38.401 --> 35:40.803
I secured 30 minutes before your lecture.

35:40.803 --> 35:41.838
Then let's finish within that.

35:42.172 --> 35:43.206
That's enough.

35:43.206 --> 35:45.074
A man like Mr. Oh...

35:45.074 --> 35:47.110
wouldn't spend too long...

35:47.110 --> 35:48.711
talking to someone he'd just met like me.

35:49.812 --> 35:50.780
(Myo Jin)

35:51.681 --> 35:52.582
Myo Jin.

35:52.582 --> 35:53.550
Sorry, but I'm in the middle of...

35:57.053 --> 35:58.855
How many times is this now?

35:59.989 --> 36:01.658
(Police Station)

36:02.125 --> 36:03.026
Myo Jin.

36:04.861 --> 36:05.728
Are you okay?

36:07.397 --> 36:08.264
Are you?

36:09.966 --> 36:11.768
That didn't happen
from riding a bike, did it?

36:18.007 --> 36:19.475
Are you Ham Myo Jin's guardian?

36:20.510 --> 36:21.344
Was it you?

36:22.078 --> 36:23.246
Did you do that to this woman?

36:23.246 --> 36:24.214
Calm down.

36:24.214 --> 36:25.448
- Jun Ho.
- Please calm down.

36:25.782 --> 36:27.517
Damn it, this is so irritating.

36:27.984 --> 36:30.286
- You little punk.
- You can't do this in here.

36:30.653 --> 36:31.454
Hey.

36:32.088 --> 36:34.390
I don't care if he's a minor.
I'm not letting him off.

36:34.757 --> 36:35.959
Handle it according to the law.

36:38.795 --> 36:39.796
Myo Jin, are you okay?

36:39.796 --> 36:41.497
Move.

36:45.268 --> 36:47.136
Why are you following someone
who killed a person?

36:47.136 --> 36:48.438
Do you want to get killed too?

37:08.124 --> 37:10.126
Did I kill someone?

37:11.427 --> 37:12.395
What?

37:12.395 --> 37:14.430
What that boy's mother said earlier...

37:16.432 --> 37:18.535
didn't sound like
she was just saying things.

37:19.335 --> 37:22.238
She's the kind of person
who slaps her kid in public.

37:23.406 --> 37:25.408
Why do you care
what someone like that says?

37:26.176 --> 37:28.678
Even if I keep seeing
someone burning to death,

37:30.146 --> 37:32.482
even if people around here
say I killed someone,

37:33.816 --> 37:35.852
am I supposed to think it's nothing?

37:38.588 --> 37:40.490
That's not what I meant.

37:40.790 --> 37:42.559
That's what the doctor said too.

37:43.660 --> 37:45.195
Any memory that comes up,

37:45.195 --> 37:46.829
I should accept as it is.

37:49.432 --> 37:51.334
But that doesn't mean
you have to believe...

37:51.334 --> 37:52.669
every cruel thing a stranger says.

37:53.303 --> 37:54.704
Then what am I supposed to believe?

37:55.471 --> 37:58.041
Did the hospital even tell us
how to tell what to trust?

37:58.374 --> 38:00.009
This is a time to be careful.

38:01.144 --> 38:02.078
Don't...

38:02.912 --> 38:04.414
overinterpret everything.

38:10.553 --> 38:11.688
Hey, he's here.

38:11.688 --> 38:12.722
He's here.

38:12.722 --> 38:14.157
Come on, over here.

38:14.157 --> 38:15.091
Right here.

38:15.959 --> 38:17.560
Pull over here.

38:19.362 --> 38:20.964
- Hurry up.
- Hurry up.

38:20.964 --> 38:22.899
- Hurry up.
- Hurry up.

38:24.367 --> 38:25.768
Hurry up.

38:25.768 --> 38:26.903
(L Karaoke Bar)

38:39.349 --> 38:41.017
Boss, we're all set.

38:41.417 --> 38:42.252
Okay.

38:49.225 --> 38:50.226
Damn it.

38:50.226 --> 38:51.394
That scared me.

38:51.394 --> 38:52.629
What was that?

38:53.429 --> 38:55.732
Gentlemen, we're closed.

38:55.999 --> 38:58.001
We need to get off work too
if we want to work again tomorrow.

38:58.501 --> 39:00.770
What is all this?

39:00.770 --> 39:03.039
We just had rice wine
and scallion pancakes at a bar.

39:03.840 --> 39:05.041
We got suckered.

39:05.041 --> 39:06.009
Suckered how?

39:06.442 --> 39:10.079
That place earlier drugged our drinks.

39:10.079 --> 39:11.014
What?

39:12.615 --> 39:13.917
You're way too suspicious.

39:16.486 --> 39:17.587
Let's see.

39:17.587 --> 39:20.089
- Room charge, band fee,
- What?

39:24.093 --> 39:26.162
and this too, so it's 3,000 per person.

39:26.529 --> 39:27.564
So 12,000 dollars.

39:28.398 --> 39:29.933
Time to settle up, gentlemen.

39:29.933 --> 39:32.602
I even took off the hostess fee
so it wouldn't be too much.

39:32.602 --> 39:33.870
What the...

39:33.870 --> 39:35.371
Are you screwing around right now?

39:35.371 --> 39:38.141
Hey, don't get tangled up.
Just call the police.

39:38.141 --> 39:39.342
- Yeah, call them.
- Yeah.

39:41.044 --> 39:41.878
Why?

39:42.579 --> 39:44.714
- Do you have your phone?
- My phone?

39:45.815 --> 39:46.683
Hey, look.

39:48.451 --> 39:50.486
Once you're done paying,
I'll send you each one...

39:50.486 --> 39:51.454
as a little souvenir.

39:56.726 --> 39:57.560
Hey.

39:58.795 --> 39:59.863
Do you want to die?

40:01.731 --> 40:02.999
Give me my phone right now.

40:04.968 --> 40:06.236
- Hey.
- Yeah?

40:06.236 --> 40:07.570
Should we flip this whole place over?

40:08.238 --> 40:11.074
Young Gu, let's have some fun!

40:13.343 --> 40:14.244
What?

40:15.144 --> 40:17.580
Are you paying or not, gentlemen?

40:21.751 --> 40:22.785
Young Gu, three minutes.

40:22.785 --> 40:23.987
Yes, boss.

40:32.829 --> 40:34.230
Hey, you punk!

40:35.532 --> 40:37.300
Hey!

40:50.113 --> 40:51.181
You bastard.

41:01.691 --> 41:03.126
Damn it.

41:04.160 --> 41:05.528
I'm in charge of the VIPs!

41:11.734 --> 41:13.837
That felt good there.

41:13.837 --> 41:14.971
Yeah, the big one.

41:15.438 --> 41:16.973
It's so big, I love it.

41:17.273 --> 41:18.041
Hey.

41:18.842 --> 41:19.709
Do you know me?

41:20.476 --> 41:22.145
Why are you staring at me?

41:22.145 --> 41:23.413
Because it's nice.

41:24.747 --> 41:27.116
Your lady is absolutely gorgeous.

41:27.750 --> 41:30.420
If you've got nothing better to do,
go home and sleep it off.

41:30.653 --> 41:31.621
Yes, sir.

41:31.621 --> 41:32.589
Damn it.

41:33.056 --> 41:34.157
Let's go.

41:34.657 --> 41:37.293
You two look great together.

41:37.293 --> 41:38.795
Let go of me. Are you crazy?

41:38.795 --> 41:40.597
Babe, calm down.

41:40.597 --> 41:41.931
She's completely insane.

41:41.931 --> 41:42.765
Seriously.

41:45.535 --> 41:47.570
Babe, who is she?

41:48.171 --> 41:49.606
Do you know that woman?

41:49.606 --> 41:51.674
How would I know her?

41:51.674 --> 41:52.675
You saw her too, didn't you?

41:52.876 --> 41:55.245
Why are you snapping at me?

41:55.879 --> 41:58.047
You should've listened to me.

41:58.047 --> 41:59.716
About what?

41:59.716 --> 42:01.584
I said we should go
to my studio apartment, didn't I?

42:01.885 --> 42:03.620
We didn't, and look what happened.

42:03.620 --> 42:05.822
That studio apartment is way too small.

42:05.822 --> 42:08.458
Then get me a bigger place.

42:08.458 --> 42:10.793
Fine. I'll buy you an apartment.

42:10.793 --> 42:11.761
Really?

42:12.161 --> 42:13.196
Yeah.

42:16.266 --> 42:17.100
What's this?

42:17.100 --> 42:19.536
(Unread Message)

42:20.136 --> 42:21.905
The photos came out great, didn't they?

42:21.905 --> 42:23.173
What is this?

42:51.034 --> 42:53.303
I was trying to let you sleep longer,

42:53.937 --> 42:55.705
but I ended up waking you instead.

42:57.307 --> 42:58.341
It's okay.

42:59.576 --> 43:00.743
Did you take your medicine
before sleeping?

43:01.444 --> 43:02.278
Yes.

43:03.880 --> 43:05.515
But when I take it,

43:05.849 --> 43:07.450
I get into a bad mood.

43:08.651 --> 43:10.253
I have nightmares,

43:11.120 --> 43:12.789
and they feel too real.

43:13.256 --> 43:14.090
Really?

43:15.425 --> 43:17.794
That's odd. It was prescribed properly.

43:18.127 --> 43:20.630
Okay, I'll call the hospital and ask.

43:35.345 --> 43:36.779
The detectives are here.

43:37.280 --> 43:39.782
They say they have questions
about your accident.

43:41.518 --> 43:43.520
I'm Detective Woo Jong Rok
from Namyeong Police Station.

43:43.520 --> 43:44.621
I'm Detective Lee Seong Tae.

43:48.625 --> 43:49.959
- Please sit down.
- Okay.

44:01.604 --> 44:03.473
She hasn't been out of the hospital
for very long,

44:03.473 --> 44:05.108
and she's still recovering.

44:05.108 --> 44:08.378
So please keep this brief.

44:08.611 --> 44:09.445
Okay.

44:10.246 --> 44:13.383
We heard from the hospital
about Ms. Ham's condition.

44:13.383 --> 44:16.519
So we'd just like to confirm a few things.

44:18.154 --> 44:19.189
The hospital?

44:19.622 --> 44:20.523
Yes.

44:20.523 --> 44:23.726
From the surgeon who handled
all of your surgeries...

44:23.726 --> 44:24.727
and treatment.

44:27.797 --> 44:28.631
I see.

44:29.799 --> 44:32.735
About the accident that happened
on Jebudo Island that day,

44:32.735 --> 44:34.037
could you tell us about it?

44:34.671 --> 44:36.039
Do you remember anything now?

44:38.474 --> 44:40.143
I still...

44:41.010 --> 44:42.545
Detective,

44:42.545 --> 44:44.380
that's a very broad question.

44:46.516 --> 44:49.118
You can just say
whatever comes to mind.

44:50.286 --> 44:53.823
If it's something from the villa
or around there,

44:53.823 --> 44:54.691
anything at all.

44:57.360 --> 44:58.795
The villa...

44:59.796 --> 45:01.531
Before dawn that day,

45:01.531 --> 45:02.999
where were you headed?

45:13.543 --> 45:14.711
Right now,

45:15.612 --> 45:16.579
my memory...

45:17.680 --> 45:20.950
Are you saying you still
don't remember the accident at all?

45:23.820 --> 45:25.188
I'm sorry.

45:25.188 --> 45:26.723
I guess I'm still not myself yet.

45:27.390 --> 45:28.324
Detective,

45:28.625 --> 45:31.761
if you're only here
to establish the basic facts...

45:32.462 --> 45:33.396
Wait.

45:37.500 --> 45:38.568
Could it be...

45:40.003 --> 45:43.273
that I caused some kind of accident there?

45:43.740 --> 45:45.308
There was an explosion
caused by a gas leak,

45:45.308 --> 45:47.143
and at the time the villa caught fire,

45:47.710 --> 45:50.480
your car overturned in an accident.

45:51.548 --> 45:53.616
The time and distance were too close...

45:54.450 --> 45:56.753
to treat them as separate incidents.

45:57.520 --> 45:58.354
What?

46:01.157 --> 46:02.125
Detective,

46:02.125 --> 46:04.127
if what you're saying is true,

46:04.127 --> 46:06.262
are you saying...

46:06.996 --> 46:08.798
she is a suspect in that case?

46:09.199 --> 46:11.634
Even a driver passing by
the accident scene...

46:12.202 --> 46:14.370
said they saw Ms. Ham's car...

46:14.370 --> 46:16.372
coming from the villa.

46:22.145 --> 46:23.246
Myo Jin, are you okay?

46:26.049 --> 46:27.851
Didn't the doctor say
not to agitate the patient?

46:27.851 --> 46:29.018
Didn't they tell you?

46:29.018 --> 46:31.688
Why do you have to do this here and now?

46:32.188 --> 46:33.289
Please leave immediately.

46:37.026 --> 46:38.194
We apologize.

46:39.095 --> 46:39.963
Ms. Ham,

46:40.263 --> 46:41.764
we hope you recover soon.

46:42.632 --> 46:43.433
Bye.

46:49.372 --> 46:50.707
Myo Jin, are you okay?

47:01.150 --> 47:02.752
This isn't some kids' game.

47:02.752 --> 47:04.053
She doesn't remember? I can't even.

47:05.488 --> 47:09.158
What if Ham Myo Jin's condition
is worse than we thought?

47:09.158 --> 47:11.828
Give me a break.

47:12.328 --> 47:13.830
How long has it been since the accident?

47:14.531 --> 47:16.065
Then why did they discharge her?

47:24.340 --> 47:25.575
I don't like this.

47:26.576 --> 47:27.844
Ham Myo Jin's accident.

47:27.844 --> 47:29.512
Go over every forensic record again.

47:29.512 --> 47:31.781
There isn't a single piece
of evidence left.

47:32.415 --> 47:33.683
I told you.

47:33.683 --> 47:35.518
They never found the car's dashcam either.

47:36.920 --> 47:39.389
What about anything attached to her body,
like clothes or shoes?

47:40.089 --> 47:42.325
They were badly damaged
during emergency treatment,

47:42.325 --> 47:43.626
so everything was disposed of.

47:45.228 --> 47:47.864
Then what am I supposed to do?

47:47.864 --> 47:48.865
Why did the chief take...

47:48.865 --> 47:50.400
a case like this?

47:50.400 --> 47:52.135
Do you think he wanted to?

47:52.135 --> 47:54.037
Team One suddenly just dropped it,

47:54.037 --> 47:55.305
so we had to take it on.

48:00.810 --> 48:01.878
Here's one.

48:03.213 --> 48:04.581
Why is even this messing with me now?

48:04.914 --> 48:07.650
You sure know how to sniff things out.

48:08.685 --> 48:09.719
What did you say?

48:09.719 --> 48:10.620
Sir.

48:12.021 --> 48:14.524
You dug up quite a bit.

48:20.830 --> 48:21.798
Settlement agreement.

48:23.833 --> 48:24.934
What is this?

48:25.602 --> 48:27.770
We settled everything yesterday
for 30,000 dollars.

48:27.770 --> 48:30.073
A settlement only becomes valid...

48:30.073 --> 48:32.108
after the money is transferred,

48:32.108 --> 48:33.209
right?

48:33.843 --> 48:35.678
- But...
- Hold on.

48:44.821 --> 48:46.856
And on top of that,
you met again yesterday too...

48:46.856 --> 48:48.992
at W Wine Bar in Cheongdam-dong.

48:50.026 --> 48:51.828
Very impressive.

48:52.662 --> 48:55.098
I can see you're very professional.

48:55.098 --> 48:57.167
I'm impressed too...

48:57.167 --> 48:58.668
at the tireless sex drive...

48:58.668 --> 49:00.803
that keeps me going.

49:01.504 --> 49:02.539
What's the secret to it?

49:03.173 --> 49:04.174
An affair?

49:05.475 --> 49:06.442
Excuse me.

49:06.776 --> 49:10.013
I'm the kind of woman
who gets DMs from idols.

49:10.847 --> 49:13.016
So stop barking up the wrong tree...

49:13.016 --> 49:14.817
and go do your job.

49:21.191 --> 49:22.158
Impressive.

49:24.827 --> 49:27.197
I don't know what you do for a living,

49:27.197 --> 49:28.731
but threatening women like this...

49:28.731 --> 49:30.633
and extorting money from them...

49:42.011 --> 49:43.346
Amazing.

49:44.447 --> 49:46.115
A hundred ten thousand followers?

49:47.016 --> 49:48.051
You're one of the cool crowd.

49:49.919 --> 49:52.355
Luxury brands, hot restaurants,

49:52.355 --> 49:53.389
and overseas trips.

49:53.890 --> 49:54.891
I'm so jealous.

49:56.759 --> 49:58.561
You old creep.

49:58.561 --> 50:00.096
I'll check out your account too.

50:01.130 --> 50:02.565
But I won't send DMs.

50:03.399 --> 50:04.834
I'll leave photos in the comments.

50:05.168 --> 50:06.135
The sexy kind.

50:19.682 --> 50:21.251
Why did it take so long?

50:23.086 --> 50:25.688
(Transfer to An Woo Sik, 20,000 dollars)

50:27.123 --> 50:28.625
I sent it. Check.

50:29.726 --> 50:30.693
Are you happy...

50:30.693 --> 50:32.462
taking 50 percent off the top
every single time?

50:32.462 --> 50:33.897
Here we go again.

50:33.897 --> 50:35.565
I'm the one who brings in all the work.

50:35.565 --> 50:37.667
Isn't this too exploitative?

50:37.667 --> 50:40.537
You still have a long way to go
before that debt is paid off.

50:41.971 --> 50:43.206
I was crazy.

50:43.540 --> 50:45.441
How did I end up with a leech like you?

50:46.209 --> 50:49.012
I'm the reason
you're starting to act human again.

50:49.245 --> 50:50.547
If I'd just left you back then,

50:50.547 --> 50:53.082
you'd have had your limbs chopped off
and be begging somewhere.

50:53.082 --> 50:53.883
Hey.

50:54.217 --> 50:55.985
Why do you have to talk like such a jerk?

50:57.153 --> 50:58.121
What, a jerk?

50:59.122 --> 51:01.357
I save some worthless punk...

51:01.357 --> 51:02.592
drowning in gambling debt,

51:02.592 --> 51:03.826
and you're calling me a jerk?

51:03.826 --> 51:05.495
You got a problem with 50 percent?

51:05.495 --> 51:08.831
I helped you with your jobs,
got found out and lost my dealer job,

51:08.831 --> 51:10.733
and right before you got stabbed,
I paid money to stop it...

51:10.733 --> 51:12.202
and even saved your ass, so what?

51:12.836 --> 51:14.404
Now you're regretting the deal?

51:15.505 --> 51:17.140
I've got your bankbook and seal,

51:17.140 --> 51:20.410
and even the promissory note
you wrote that day.

51:20.944 --> 51:22.378
So go ahead and try something.

51:23.112 --> 51:25.481
If I sell you off
to loan sharks for extra cash,

51:25.481 --> 51:27.784
you'll be shipped
straight to a fishing boat galley.

51:27.784 --> 51:29.452
Whatever.

51:30.453 --> 51:31.754
You know my bad luck streak
is over now, right?

51:32.655 --> 51:35.191
(Ryu Jun Ho)

51:35.191 --> 51:36.993
Your bad luck may be over,

51:37.760 --> 51:40.096
but my luck's finally turning.

51:41.331 --> 51:42.165
What?

51:46.169 --> 51:47.504
The color turned out nice.

51:47.504 --> 51:48.538
But I guess I should cover it.

51:49.572 --> 51:50.540
What a waste.

51:58.181 --> 51:59.649
(When will my memory come back?)

51:59.649 --> 52:01.117
(Who was the person in my dream?)

52:01.117 --> 52:02.385
(Explosion?)

52:02.385 --> 52:04.120
(Why can't I remem...)

52:23.206 --> 52:24.474
Yesterday, in the woods,

52:25.808 --> 52:29.045
there was a boy who tried to steal my bag.

52:29.045 --> 52:30.280
Let go! Let go of my bag!

52:30.280 --> 52:31.047
You little...

52:34.350 --> 52:35.952
He lives around here.

52:37.620 --> 52:40.590
After fighting with him,
I ended up at the police station.

52:41.591 --> 52:42.725
His mother...

52:44.394 --> 52:46.829
spoke as if I'd killed someone,

52:49.933 --> 52:52.202
and everyone looked like..

52:54.704 --> 52:56.973
they already knew it was true.

52:58.107 --> 53:00.043
Why are you following someone
who killed a person?

53:00.043 --> 53:01.411
Do you want to get killed too?

53:05.615 --> 53:07.851
The detectives came today.

53:08.785 --> 53:11.221
They thought it was strange...

53:11.821 --> 53:13.289
that I still remember nothing.

53:15.425 --> 53:16.292
No.

53:17.293 --> 53:18.895
They were suspicious of me.

53:19.362 --> 53:22.565
Are you saying you still
don't remember the accident at all?

53:24.934 --> 53:27.337
They think the villa burned down
and someone died...

53:31.374 --> 53:33.610
because of me.

53:36.880 --> 53:39.616
Can you tell me why you think that?

53:40.149 --> 53:41.150
It's just...

53:42.852 --> 53:44.821
I feel like...

53:44.821 --> 53:46.890
I did something terribly wrong.

53:48.691 --> 53:50.760
No matter how I think about it,

53:52.495 --> 53:54.664
memory isn't what's tormenting me.

53:55.231 --> 53:57.400
Then what do you think it is?

53:57.767 --> 53:59.669
I think it's emotion.

54:02.138 --> 54:04.641
I keep seeing a woman burn to death,

54:05.175 --> 54:07.177
and the man who tried to kill me
in my dream...

54:07.177 --> 54:08.344
also feels so real,

54:10.680 --> 54:11.948
like I was there...

54:12.815 --> 54:14.617
with those people...

54:14.617 --> 54:16.286
in that place.

54:17.954 --> 54:19.522
Even after returning home...

54:19.522 --> 54:21.624
to live with the man I'm engaged to,

54:23.927 --> 54:25.495
I can't shake the feeling...

54:26.196 --> 54:27.730
that something is wrong.

54:28.364 --> 54:29.265
This...

54:30.233 --> 54:32.235
is a different problem from memory.

54:32.769 --> 54:34.771
It's okay. Go on.

54:38.975 --> 54:40.543
If I keep doing this counseling...

54:42.212 --> 54:44.447
and endure treatment,

54:47.317 --> 54:48.651
then someday,

54:50.420 --> 54:51.855
my memory will come back, right?

54:53.289 --> 54:54.324
Of course.

54:59.963 --> 55:00.897
Doctor.

55:07.303 --> 55:08.438
We're engaged.

55:09.005 --> 55:10.840
- Do you remember?
- I don't remember...

55:12.742 --> 55:13.910
anything.

55:16.779 --> 55:19.516
There's one thing
I've learned about myself.

55:19.516 --> 55:22.151
It feels more like emotion than memory.

55:22.485 --> 55:25.421
From the moment I woke up in the hospital,

55:27.457 --> 55:29.058
I wanted my memory to come back,

55:30.560 --> 55:32.562
but I've only grown more helpless.

55:35.465 --> 55:36.332
Our house.

55:38.001 --> 55:39.335
Our house.

55:40.770 --> 55:41.905
It's meaningless.

55:42.772 --> 55:44.274
This kind of waiting.

55:48.178 --> 55:49.179
I won't do it any longer.

55:51.381 --> 55:53.716
I'm done waiting for my memory.

56:30.332 --> 56:35.148
(REVERSE)

56:35.325 --> 56:36.326
Tell me clearly.

56:36.326 --> 56:37.994
Who exactly are they saying I killed?

56:38.228 --> 56:39.562
Did you ever imagine...

56:39.562 --> 56:42.198
someone could commit murder
in that blazing inferno?

56:42.198 --> 56:43.566
But you seemed very close.

56:43.566 --> 56:45.168
You're talking about Hee Su, right?

56:45.168 --> 56:46.736
I want to know who she is.

56:46.736 --> 56:49.372
I don't think
she was that important a friend.

56:49.372 --> 56:50.507
Ms. Ham.

56:50.507 --> 56:53.009
Isn't she worse off than what you told me?

56:53.009 --> 56:54.811
That's why it's dangerous.

56:54.811 --> 56:55.678
Blackmail?

56:55.678 --> 56:57.780
This is the person you hired.

56:57.780 --> 57:00.550
Myo Jin is acting out of character.

57:00.550 --> 57:02.151
You need to bleed too.

57:03.373 --> 57:05.373
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
